        <abstract>
            <p>Discusses at length CL’s criticisms of natural selection.</p>
            <p>Comments on possible former connection between the Galapagos and South America.</p>
            <p>Discounts survival of mammals on atolls.</p>
            <p>Discusses reptile origin of mammals.</p>
            <p>Discounts development of a mammal on an island and the descent of mammals from a bird.</p>
            <p>The antiquity of islands.</p> 
<p>Comments on bats of New Zealand. Geographical distribution of seals. Discusses <hi rend="italic">Amblyrhynchus</hi>.</p>  
<p>Glad CL will read his MS on origin of dogs [<hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> 1: 15–43].</p> 
        </abstract>
